data.description: ATTENTION ALL Investors/ Handyman- Amazing potential with this 3 bedroom ranch with a unique layout in and out that comes with 2 LOTS TOTAL. Long Driveway! New furnace(2022), New windows on east wing(2022), New water heater (2022), New water softener(2022). Dividing the 2 wings is the steps to the Lower level. The West wing features a huge Family/Party Rm-perfect for that pool table or Big Screen TV for Football parties, has a separate heater, Kitchenette and 2nd Bathroom project that needs to be finished. Basement is unfinished but studded, leads to exterior Access. Seller is offering it AS-IS.
